From cb83d689047087c25b2ae9899a752312dabac503 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ruben <rubenmeister@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 21 Mar 2026 16:41:28 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] feat(auth): unified auth system with role-based access
 control
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Backend: add guide, operator, corporate to RoleType and validators
- Webapp: fix NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL env, add RoleGuard component
- Webapp: protect provider routes (conductores, anfitriones, operadores)
- Webapp: rename Guía Local → Promotor Local (/promotores-locales)
- Webapp: update register labels (Usuario, Anfitrión solo alojamiento)
- Webapp: add account notice in /envios/cotizar
- Admin dashboard: enforce admin role check at login + auth context
- Corporate portal: fix NextAuth authorize response shape mapping
- Mobile user app: persist full user in AsyncStorage on login/register
- Mobile driver app: validate driver role at login, persist user data

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
