+              📚 Ir a la Academia Going
+            </Link>
+            <Link href="/"
+              className="block w-full py-3 rounded-xl font-bold text-gray-700 text-center bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
+              Volver al inicio
